      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# 🎬 AUTO MOVIE DIRECTOR — Type An Idea, Get A Movie\n\n## FASTEST — Type your movie idea in the big box on the Movie Planner, set the mode switch to \"3) Auto Movie\", press Queue. Done. Script, scenes, camera work, sound and editing all happen on their own — the finished MP4 plays right on the node.\n\n## WANT TO CHECK IT FIRST? — Mode \"1) Storyboard\" gives you one picture per scene in minutes. Happy? Flip to \"2) Storyboard To Movie\" and every scene starts on the exact picture you approved.\n\n## MAKE IT YOURS — Scene count, seconds per scene and style are on the Planner. Type into any scene's own box to override the AI; leave it blank and the AI writes that scene.\n"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
